{"title":"CSS Grid Layout 用法","date":"2021-01-16T12:18:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年1月16日","L":"2021/01/16","MM-DD":"01-16"},"link":"post/2021/202101/CSS-Grid-Layout","categories":["CSS相关"],"updated":"2022-04-11T03:41:31.970Z","content":"<p>相关参考文档:<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\" target=\"_blank\">CSS Grid Layout</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"grid-layout-相关概念\">grid layout 相关概念<a title=\"#grid-layout-相关概念\" href=\"#grid-layout-相关概念\"></a></h2>\n<p>和 felxbox布局一样 在使用grid布局之前 同样需要先了解一下相关的概念,这些概念在 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\" target=\"_blank\">Basic Concepts of grid layout</a>一文当中有相对详细的解释:</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid\" target=\"_blank\">Grid</a></strong>: 一种二维布局模型</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout#the_implicit_and_explicit_grid\" target=\"_blank\">Explicit Grid</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout#the_implicit_and_explicit_grid\" target=\"_blank\">Implicit Grid</a></strong>:</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout#the_grid_container\" target=\"_blank\">Grid Container</a></strong>: 当你把一个元素的display属性设置为 grid/inline-grid 则这个元素就会变成 grid contianer<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">Grid Item</a></strong>: grid container 的直接子元素就会变成 grid item</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Lines\" target=\"_blank\">Grid Lines</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Tracks\" target=\"_blank\">Grid Tracks</a></strong>: 网格轨道 是 位于2个相邻的 grid line 之间的空间.<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">Grid Cell</a></strong>: grid cell 是 css grid 当中的最小单元,他是4个 grid line 相交组成的空间,在概念上 和table 当中的 table cell 很相似.<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas\" target=\"_blank\">Grid Areas</a></strong>: grid area 是一个或多个 grid cell 构成的举行区域,当你 在grid container当中通过 line-based placement 方式放置 grid item的时候  grid area 会被创建, 或者 你也可以通过 grid-template-areas 直接创建 grid area.<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\" target=\"_blank\">Gutters</a></strong>: gutters表示grid tracks 之间的距离, 可以通过 column-gap,row-gap,gap进行控制, 当然也可以通过margin padding 等进行控制.<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Axis\" target=\"_blank\">Grid Axis</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Rows\" target=\"_blank\">Grid row</a></strong>: 水平的grid track 就是 grid row<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Column\" target=\"_blank\">Grid column</a></strong>: 垂直的 grid track 就是grid column</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在讲解下面的属性之前 我先讲一下 grid item 是如何在 grid container当中被放置的:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"grid-container-相关css属性\">grid container 相关CSS属性<a title=\"#grid-container-相关css属性\" href=\"#grid-container-相关css属性\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" target=\"_blank\">grid-template-columns</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" target=\"_blank\">grid-template-rows</a></strong>:</p>\n<details><summary>更多相关细节</summary><p>🥱 You got me !</p>\n</details><p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" target=\"_blank\">grid-template-areas</a></strong>:</p>\n<details><summary>更多相关细节</summary><p>🥱 You got me !</p>\n</details><p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\" target=\"_blank\">grid-template</a></strong>: CSS简写属性用来定义 grid columns, grid rows 和 grid areas.</p>\n<details><summary>更多相关细节</summary><p>🥱 You got me !</p>\n</details><hr>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" target=\"_blank\">grid-auto-columns</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" target=\"_blank\">grid-auto-rows</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" target=\"_blank\">grid-auto-flow</a></strong>:</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" target=\"_blank\">column-gap(grid-row-gap)</a></strong>: 同 flexbox layout column-gap<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" target=\"_blank\">row-gap(grid-column-gap)</a></strong>: 同 flexbox layout row-gap<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/gap\" target=\"_blank\">gap(grid-gap)</a></strong>: 同 flexbox layout gap</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\" target=\"_blank\">grid</a></strong>: CSS简写属性 可以同时设置所有的 隐式grid 和显示grid 的grid 属性</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong><a href=\"#\">justify-items</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">align-items</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">place-items</a></strong>:</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"#\">justify-content</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">align-content</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"#\">place-content</a></strong>:</p>\n<h2 id=\"grid-item-相关css属性\">grid item 相关CSS属性<a title=\"#grid-item-相关css属性\" href=\"#grid-item-相关css属性\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\" target=\"_blank\">grid-column-start</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\" target=\"_blank\">grid-column-end</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\" target=\"_blank\">grid-column</a></strong>: CSS简写属性 最多可以接收2个值, 第1个给grid-column-start 第2个给grid-column-end用/分开.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\" target=\"_blank\">grid-row-start</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\" target=\"_blank\">grid-row-end</a></strong>:<br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\" target=\"_blank\">grid-row</a></strong>: CSS简写属性 最多可以接收2个值,第1个给grid-row-start,第2个给grid-row-end,用/分开.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\" target=\"_blank\">grid-area</a></strong>:</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong><a href=\"\">justify-self</a></strong><br>\n<strong><a href=\"\">align-self</a></strong><br>\n<strong><a href=\"\">place-self</a></strong></p>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS box-shadow样式生成器","link":"post/2021/202101/BoxShadow样式生成器"},"next":{"title":"CSS Flexible Box Layout用法","link":"post/2021/202101/CSS-Flexible-Box-Layout"},"plink":"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS-Grid-Layout/","toc":[{"id":"grid-layout-相关概念","title":"grid layout 相关概念","index":"1"},{"id":"grid-container-相关css属性","title":"grid container 相关CSS属性","index":"2"},{"id":"grid-item-相关css属性","title":"grid item 相关CSS属性","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"李攀攀","link":"<a href=\"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS-Grid-Layout/\" title=\"CSS Grid Layout 用法\">http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS-Grid-Layout/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"},"reading_time":"570 字约 4 分钟"}